# plot
plt.figure(figsize=(10,6), dpi=130)
for x in range(1000):
    sim_ret = np.random.normal(mu, sigma , 252)
    sim_prices = initial * (sim_ret + 1).cumprod()
    plt.axhline(initial)
    plt.plot(sim_prices)
